      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31937941">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49582834/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49582834-1.jpg" alt="落叶维扬" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31937941/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31937941/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49582834/" class=" " title="落叶维扬">落叶维扬</a>
                (一剑任天真)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31937941">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我曾以为《红楼梦》是前无古人后无来着上下三百年无出其右的文学作品，直到看过了《金瓶梅》，才知道那是过去的自己见识浅薄。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-06-16 09:55</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                我曾以为《红楼梦》是前无古人后无来着上下三百年无出其右的文学作品，直到看过了《金瓶梅》，才知道那是过去的自己见识浅薄。
